{"tid":1201872,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"野餐買左好多料，係街比龜問話，是咪事必要答?","createTime":"2019-06-11T06:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:34:01.000Z","uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39066e39ec7db45c7922e6ccfe8e9bb4d4bad5d1","tid":1201872,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"有friend話係SSP見到D龜會隨街搵D個袋裝好多野既人問話。準備去買料，如果比龜問，法律角度出發點答最好"},{"pid":"6e729b060dc60f70f882eda66886cde8c8d7783a","tid":1201872,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"如果佢要搜身或者袋，可否拒絕或要求律師在場監督<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap232!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap232%21zh-Hant-HK&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=d34be785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap232!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n第232章《警隊條例》第54-55條<br />\n<br />\n54.截停、扣留及搜查的權力<br />\n(1)警務人員如在任何街道或其他公眾地方、或於任何船隻或交通工具上，不論日夜任何時間，發現任何人行動可疑，該警務人員採取以下行動，乃屬合法 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)截停該人以要求他<span style=\"color: red;\">出示身分證明文件</span>供該警務人員查閱；<br />\n(b)<span style=\"color: red;\">扣留</span>該人一段合理期間，在該期間內由該警務人員<span style=\"color: red;\">查究</span>該人是否涉嫌在任何時候犯了任何罪行；及<br />\n(c)如該警務人員認為以下行動乃屬必需 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)向該人<span style=\"color: red;\">搜查任何可能對該警務人員構成危險的東西</span>；及<br />\n(ii)扣留該人一段為作出該項搜查而合理需要的期間。"},{"pid":"dfcd6924502c5498304381b6438969b794d44913","tid":1201872,"uid":13688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"BBQ都要問過警察俾唔俾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6964f16827a692b5eda814c51c124332bbcb1755","tid":1201872,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}